headline: AutoZone Vendor Summit Recognizes Contributions of Top Suppliers
summary: MEMPHIS, Tenn., June 12, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- AutoZone (NYSE: AZO) recognized 18 of its top suppliers at its annual Vendor Summit. The awards recognize companies that have delivered exceptional performance and demonstrated a strong commitment to customer satisfaction over the past year.
